msgid "If an enemy is drawn from the exploration deck, it is resolved as normal. If it is discarded, place it in the encounter discard pile as you would normally. This is considered an \"unsuccessful\" exploration."
msgstr "如果从探索牌堆抽取了敌人，如常结算。如果该卡牌被弃掉，如常将它放到遭遇弃牌堆。这视为一次“失败”的探索。"

msgid "In some scenarios, there are additional changes to the explore rules. These changes are noted on the setup card for each scenario."
msgstr "在某些冒险中，探索规则会有额外改动。这些改动会在每个冒险的冒险设置卡牌上写明。"

msgid "Why Did It Have to Be Snakes?"
msgstr "为什么非得是蛇？"

msgid "Defeat twenty [[Serpent]] enemies."
msgstr "击败20个[[蛇族]]敌人。"

msgid "Watch Them Unravel"
msgstr "看著它们渐渐解开"

msgid "Complete all four act decks during a single playthrough of “Threads of Fate.”"
msgstr "在单次“命运之线”冒险期间完成所有4个场景牌堆。"

msgid "Hope for Humanity"
msgstr "人类还有希望"

msgid "Restore Ichtaca’s faith in humanity in “The Boundary Beyond.”"
msgstr "在“界限彼端”中，让伊塔卡重振对人类的信念。"

msgid "Scenario 5-What?"
msgstr "冒险5-什么？"

msgid "Skip “Heart of the Elders, Part 1.”"
msgstr "跳过“久远腹地，第一章”。"

msgid "Beyond Perfection:"
msgstr "超越完美"

msgid "Complete all eight tasks on act 2 of “The City of Archives” during a single playthrough."
msgstr "在单次“天机之城”冒险期间完成场景2的所有8项任务。"

msgid "I Remember Everything"
msgstr "我都想起来了！"

msgid "Restore Alejandro’s memories in “The City of Archives.”"
msgstr "在“天机之城”中，恢复亚历山卓的记忆。"

msgid "Patricide"
msgstr "弑父"

msgid "Defeat Yig in “The Depths of Yoth.”"
msgstr "在“破碎永世”中，击败伊格。"

msgid "He's Got a Point"
msgstr "他说得有道理"

msgid "Side with Alejandro in “Shattered Aeons.”"
msgstr "在“破碎永世”中，选择支持亚历山卓。"

msgid "Valusia Sounds Great"
msgstr "瓦卢西亚听起来不错"

msgid "Side with Ichtaca in “Shattered Aeons.”"
msgstr "在“破碎永世”中，选择支持伊塔卡。"

msgid "I’ve Built Up An Immunity"
msgstr "我已经免疫了"

msgid "Win <i>The Forgotten Age</i> campaign without ever becoming poisoned."
msgstr "在从未中毒的情况下获得《失落的时代》剧本的胜利。"

msgid "We Have an Understanding"
msgstr "我们互相理解"

msgid "Win <i>The Forgotten Age</i> campaign without ever dealing any damage to the Harbinger of Valusia."
msgstr "在从未对瓦卢西亚的预示者造成任何伤害的情况下获得《失落的时代》剧本的胜利。"

msgid "Who Needs Any of This Junk?"
msgstr "谁需要这些垃圾？"

msgid "Win <i>The Forgotten Age</i> campaign without purchasing any supplies."
msgstr "在从未购买任何补给品的情况下获得《失落的时代》剧本的胜利。"

msgid "Don’t Tread on Me"
msgstr "别踩到我"

msgid "Win <i>The Forgotten Age</i> campaign with no tally marks recorded under Yig’s Fury in your Campaign Log"
msgstr "在你冒险日志的“伊格之怒”下方没有记录的情况下获得《失落的时代》剧本的胜利。"

msgid "Bane of Yig"
msgstr "伊格之祸"

msgid "Win <i>The Forgotten Age</i> campaign with 25+ tally marks recorded under Yig’s Fury in your Campaign Log."
msgstr "在你冒险日志的“伊格之怒”下方记录次数大于等于25次的情况下获得《失落的时代》剧本的胜利。"

msgid "If I Could Turn Back Time"
msgstr "如果我能让时间倒流"

msgid "Forge your own path, unlock Scenario IX, and win <i>The Forgotten Age</i> campaign."
msgstr "开辟属于你自己的道路，解锁冒险IX，并获得《失落的时代》剧本的胜利。"

msgid "Yoth Expertise"
msgstr "幽嘶专家"

msgid "Win <i>The Forgotten Age</i> campaign on Expert difficulty"
msgstr "在专家难度下获得《失落的时代》剧本的胜利。"
